
First Try
----------
To test start with mm to create a working problem
hf2.c is using the new functions.

Using Serial number
-------------------
The selSer.c uses the serial number to find the device. Note that the 
description can be used as well, but if not then set it to NULL (char *descriptor= NULL;)

The serial number can be found by:
   sudo lsusb -v -d 0x403: | grep iSerial


